@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_chbmgo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(0.44)
    v0 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.03 - tmp + 0.03)) + wp.abs((v1 + 0.72 / tmp + 0.67)))
    v0 = 0.68
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos((tmp + 0.79 * tmp + 0.78)))
    v1 = wp.exp(((v2 + 0.50 * v1 + 0.26) - wp.cos(v0 + 0.82)))
    v0 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
